{"id":143,"parent_id":141,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":143,"title":"1 Corinthians 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","The gospel is preached by the power of the Spirit—The Spirit reveals all things to the Saints—The unrepentant natural man cannot receive the things of the Spirit of God."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.1","order":"03.09.002.16842"},["b","1"],"And I, brethren, when I came to you, came not with excellency of speech or of wisdom, declaring unto you the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"testimony"],"of God."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.2","order":"03.09.002.16843"},["b","2"],"For I determined not to know any thing among you,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"save"],"Jesus Christ, and him",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"crucified"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.3","order":"03.09.002.16844"},["b","3"],"And I was with you in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"weakness"],", and in fear, and in much trembling."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.4","order":"03.09.002.16845"},["b","4"],"And my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"speech"],"and my preaching",["i","was"],"not with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"enticing"],"words of man’s wisdom, but in demonstration of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"Spirit"],"and of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"power"],":"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.5","order":"03.09.002.16846"},["b","5"],"That your faith should not stand in the wisdom of men, but in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"power"],"of God."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.6","order":"03.09.002.16847"},["b","6"],"Howbeit we speak wisdom among them that are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"perfect"],": yet not the wisdom of this world, nor of the princes of this world, that come to nought:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.7","order":"03.09.002.16848"},["b","7"],"But we speak the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"wisdom"],"of God in a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"mystery"],",",["i","even"],"the hidden",["i",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"wisdom"],","],"which God",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"ordained"],"before the world unto our glory:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.8","order":"03.09.002.16849"},["b","8"],"Which none of the princes of this world knew: for had they known",["i","it,"],"they would not have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"crucified"],"the Lord of glory."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.9","order":"03.09.002.16850"},["b","9"],"But as it is written,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Eye"],"hath not seen, nor ear heard, neither have entered into the heart of man, the things which God hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"prepared"],"for them that love him."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.10","order":"03.09.002.16851"},["b","10"],"But God hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"revealed"],["i","them"],"unto us by his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"Spirit"],": for the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"Spirit"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"searcheth"],"all things, yea, the deep things of God."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.11","order":"03.09.002.16852"},["b","11"],"For what man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"knoweth"],"the things of a man, save the spirit of man which is in him? even so the things of God",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"knoweth"],"no man,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"but"],"the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"Spirit"],"of God."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.12","order":"03.09.002.16853"},["b","12"],"Now we have received, not the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"spirit"],"of the world, but the spirit which is of God; that we might know the things that are freely given to us of God."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.13","order":"03.09.002.16854"},["b","13"],"Which things also we speak, not in the words which man’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"wisdom"],"teacheth, but which the Holy Ghost",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"teacheth"],"; comparing spiritual things with spiritual."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.14","order":"03.09.002.16855"},["b","14"],"But the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"natural man"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"receiveth"],"not the things of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"Spirit"],"of God: for they are",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"foolishness"],"unto him: neither can he",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_14e"},"know"],["i","them,"],"because they are",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_14f"},"spiritually"],["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_14g"},"discerned"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.15","order":"03.09.002.16856"},["b","15"],"But he that is spiritual",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"judgeth"],"all things, yet he himself is judged of no man."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.16","order":"03.09.002.16857"},["b","16"],"For who hath known the mind of the Lord, that he may",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"instruct"],"him? But we have the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"mind"],"of Christ."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.1a","order":"03.09.002.16858"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/testimony"},"TG Testimony"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.2a","order":"03.09.002.16860"},["b","2a"],["span.small","GR"],"except."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.2b","order":"03.09.002.16862"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-crucifixion-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Crucifixion of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.3a","order":"03.09.002.16864"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/4.13"},"Gal. 4:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.23.23-29"},"Ether 12:23 (23–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.4a","order":"03.09.002.16866"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/1.5"},"1 Thes. 1:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.4b","order":"03.09.002.16868"},["b","4b"],["span.small","GR"],"persuasive."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.4c","order":"03.09.002.16870"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teaching-with-the-spirit"},"TG Teaching with the Spirit"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.4d","order":"03.09.002.16872"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.4.3-5"},"2 Ne. 28:4 (3–5)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-power-of"},"TG Priesthood, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.5a","order":"03.09.002.16874"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.7"},"2 Cor. 4:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.6a","order":"03.09.002.16876"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/perfection"},"TG Perfection"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.7a","order":"03.09.002.16878"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wisdom"},"TG Wisdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.7b","order":"03.09.002.16880"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mysteries-of-godliness"},"TG Mysteries of Godliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.7c","order":"03.09.002.16882"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.3"},"Col. 2:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.7d","order":"03.09.002.16884"},["b","7d"],["span.small","GR"],"foreordained."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.8a","order":"03.09.002.16886"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scripture